# .depobituaryignore - packages to exclude from health check failures
#
# One package name per line. Supports wildcard suffix (*).
# These packages will still be scored and shown in reports,
# but won't cause CI to fail.
#
# Common reasons to ignore:
# - Spec-complete libraries (UUID, JWT, compression)
# - Transitive deps locked by upstream (can't replace)
# - Go stdlib extensions (golang.org/x/*)
#
# Examples:
# github.com/google/uuid
# github.com/Azure/*
# golang.org/x/*
